# {{ project_name }}

A PyInert application using `.pi` single-file route components.

## Structure

```text
app/routes/index.pi          -> /
app/routes/about.pi          -> /about
app/routes/users/index.pi    -> /users
app/routes/users/[id].pi     -> /users/<id>
templates/app.html           -> application shell/layout
```

```html
<?py
layout("app")
title("Dashboard")
items = ["one", "two"]
?>

<h1>{{ title }}</h1>
```

Run:

```bash
python app/app.py
```
